Even though my world is #silent I will fight for those who's voices are #Silenced 
We all have a unique way to impact. If we compare ourselves to how others achieve, how others learn, how others think, grow up, & assume we know intentions/thoughts; we don't leave room to show the world that being 'different' leads to making a #DIFFERENCE.
.
If there were 10 people on earth, and you tore 9 of them down and spoke poorly of 9 to elate yourself, you didn't impact 1 person positively - you degraded 9 in the eyes of the 1. Sometimes our biggest oppressors are right beside us, so don't compare yourself to your neighbor. 
Remember ... we have different talents. We were born for different #purposes. .
There is no perfect moment - there is no perfection in humanity/timing, you just have to jump.  All the BEST things lack perfect understanding. .
#Curiosity fuels #humanity and #perfection would eliminate curiosity. Just jump. It's better to have metaphorically died than to wear a parachute your entire life wondering if it works.
